<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.9.4">
<l>aṇṭamu meṇṭicai yumnila ṉumalai nīroṭu vāṉeri kālmutalā</l>
<l>vuṇṭava ṉentaipi rāṉati ṭamoḷi māṭaṅkaḷ cūḻntaḻa kāyakacci</l>
<l>viṇṭava riṇṭai<supplied>k</supplied>ku  ḻāmuṭa ṉēvirain tāriri yacceru vilmuṉintu</l>
<l>paṇṭoru kālvaḷait tāṉpaṇin tapara mēccura viṇṇaka ramatuvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In fair Kacci encircled by shimmering mansions, the place of our father,</l>
<l rend="indent">the lord who consumed</l>
<l>The firmament, the eight directions, the earth, crashing seas,</l>
<l rend="indent">the sky, fire, wind, and so on,</l>
<l>Is Paramēccura Viṇṇakaram where bowed the one who once long ago,</l>
<l>Raging in battle, obstructed the enemy so to scatter those</l>
<l rend="indent">who hastened altogether [in] the ‘lotus’ formation.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
